Set Name TEMP
Set Size 96 81
Set Background Color black
Set Decorations off
Set Position -0 540
Set Layer Below
Set Sticky on
Set SkipTaskbar on
Set SkipPager on

Rectangle 0 0 96 81 #555555


SetEnv get "wget -o /dev/null -O - http://weather.sh.cvut.cz/export/teplota.php" Overwrite

Text 300 3 0 90 33 #a0a0a0 DejaVuSansCondensed-Bold/8 "SH %.1f °C" Alignment Center
+ exec:${get}:readline:0:scanf:n:"%f"


